<body style="padding: 24px; background: #ffffff; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2;">
  <div id="output">
<section class="container" style="text-align: left; font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB , Microsoft YaHei UI , Microsoft YaHei ,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-weight: 400; background-color: rgba(250, 249, 245, 1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01); border-radius: 25px; padding: 12px 12px;"><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all; margin-top: 0 !important;">很多人现在都在用 Claude Code。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">但大多数人的用法，其实还停留在一个很初级的阶段：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 写一句 prompt</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 看看结果</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 不满意就改改措辞</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 再试一次</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">有时候确实能成。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">但这更像是撞运气，而不是做工程。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">真正会把 Claude Code 用出生产力的人，靠的不是“更会写 prompt”，而是<strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">开始把 Claude 放进一套系统里工作</strong>。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><img src="illustrations/01-cover-wide.png" data-local-path="D:\AI\astro-blog-cn\wechat-output\suryanshti777-2048055574185779638\illustrations\01-cover-wide.png" style="display: block; width: 100%; margin: 1.5em auto;"></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这篇文章最值得看的地方，不在于它又讲了多少提示词技巧，而在于它明确说清楚了一个转变：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Claude 不是给开发者用的聊天机器人，它更像一个可编排的推理引擎。</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">一旦你换成这个视角，很多事情就会完全不一样。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文里最尖锐的一句，是这层意思：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">很多人看起来在用 Claude Code，实际上只是在“和它聊天”。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">他们的工作流通常是这样的：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 提一个需求</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 等 Claude 输出</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 发现不理想</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 继续补一句说明</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 再改一轮说法</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这个模式的问题在于，它把结果高度绑定在“这次 prompt 恰好写得对不对”上。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">所以它会出现一种很常见的错觉：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 这次很好用</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 下次怎么又不行了</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 明明是差不多的任务，为什么结果忽好忽坏</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原因并不神秘。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">因为你得到的只是一次输出，而不是一个稳定系统。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><img src="illustrations/02-chat-vs-system.png" data-local-path="D:\AI\astro-blog-cn\wechat-output\suryanshti777-2048055574185779638\illustrations\02-chat-vs-system.png" style="display: block; width: 100%; margin: 1.5em auto;"></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文里那句总结非常值得记住：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Prompts give outputs. Systems give consistency.</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">翻成中文就是：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Prompt 只能给你一次结果，系统才能给你稳定结果。</strong></p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">真正的变化：从写 Prompt，变成设计系统</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">所以，高手和普通用户的差别，往往不在于谁更会“润色提示词”，而在于有没有开始主动设计下面这些东西：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 上下文怎么组织</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 约束怎么明确</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 推理步骤怎么固定</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 错误怎么回流</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 记忆怎么保存</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">你可以把它理解成一个升级：</p><h3 class="h3" data-heading="true" style="padding-left: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #A93226; border-radius: 2px; margin: 0 8px 10px; color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.2;">旧方式</h3><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">Write → Debug → Rewrite</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">先让 Claude 写，出错了你再修，再不行就重来。</p><h3 class="h3" data-heading="true" style="padding-left: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #A93226; border-radius: 2px; margin: 0 8px 10px; color: #3f3f3f; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.2;">新方式</h3><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">Design → Generate → Test → Refine</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">先设计环境和规则，再让 Claude 生成，再通过测试和反馈循环持续收敛。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这不是“提示词工程”的小修小补，而是直接换了一层工作方法。</p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">Claude Code 的正确工作流，长什么样？</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文给出的结构非常清楚：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Input → Reasoning → Execution → Feedback → Memory</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><img src="illustrations/03-architecture-flow.png" data-local-path="D:\AI\astro-blog-cn\wechat-output\suryanshti777-2048055574185779638\illustrations\03-architecture-flow.png" style="display: block; width: 100%; margin: 1.5em auto;"></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">也就是说，一个真正像样的 Claude 工作流，不是只看“输入”和“输出”，而是至少应该包含这 5 层。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">下面我们按这个结构拆开讲。</p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">1. Input Layer：输入不是一句话，而是结构化上下文</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文一开始就指出一个关键问题：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">大多数人给 Claude 的输入，太像“临时对话”，不像“工程任务”。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">比如：</p><blockquote class="blockquote" style="margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; font-style: normal; padding: 15px 0; margin: 12px 0; border-left: 7px solid #E4B1A0; border-radius: 10px; color: #3f3f3f; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);"><p class="p" style="line-height: 2; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all; display: block; font-size: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; margin: 0;">Build a login system</p></blockquote><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这种说法的问题是，它几乎把所有重要信息都留白了。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">更成熟的方式，是把输入拆成几个稳定部分：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• Task：要做什么</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• Context：当前项目环境是什么</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• Constraints：有哪些规则不能破</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• Instructions：应该按什么步骤思考</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• Output format：结果要按什么结构返回</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这就意味着，你不再是在“手写 prompt”，而是在“生成 prompt 模板”。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文那句我很喜欢：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">You’re not writing prompts anymore. You’re generating them.</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这句话背后的意思是：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">当你开始把输入标准化，你其实已经不再依赖灵感，而是在搭可复用的输入系统。</p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">2. Reasoning Layer：不要直接要代码，先强制它思考</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文的第二层也非常重要。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">Claude 当然可以直接写代码，但直接要代码，往往会带来两个问题：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 它可能跳过边界情况</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 它可能在逻辑没想清时就开始实现</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">所以作者建议，在写代码前，先强制 Claude 做这几步：</p><ol class="ol" style="padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">1. 拆解问题</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">2. 列出可能的边界情况</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">3. 选择最优方案</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">4. 然后再生成代码</li></ol><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">看起来只是多写了几句要求，但实际效果会非常大。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">因为如果你不在前面约束推理结构，后面你就得在 bug 上补课。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文这句很有力：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">If you don’t guide the thinking, you’ll debug the output later.</strong></p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">3. Execution Layer：Claude 负责生成，但你不能裸信</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">第三层讲的是执行。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文并不反对让 Claude 生成代码，反而默认这件事应该发生。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">但作者强调：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Claude 的输出不能被“裸信任”，而应该被包在一个你自己控制的执行层里。</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">也就是说，它负责生成，但不代表它的每一行输出都自动等于最终结果。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这层的价值在于：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 你可以控制调用方式</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 可以统一格式</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 可以在外层加测试、日志和补丁机制</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这一步看起来只是“包一层 wrapper”，其实是在把 AI 从一次性工具，变成一个可集成的工程节点。</p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">4. Feedback Loop：这才是 Claude Code 真正开始变强的地方</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">如果说前面三层是在“让 Claude 更会做”，那第四层才是真正让它从工具变成系统的转折点。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文的核心思路是：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">不要让人手动去修每次失败，而要让失败自动回流。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">也就是：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 跑测试</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 发现报错</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 把错误日志喂回 Claude</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 让它修</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 再跑一次</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这就是一个最基础的“测试 -&gt; 修复 -&gt; 重试”闭环。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">你会发现，真正强的不是 Claude 单次写得多好，而是：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">系统能不能在失败后自己继续推进。</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文里有一句话，基本点透了全文：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">This is where Claude stops being a tool and becomes a system.</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">翻成中文就是：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">从这里开始，Claude 不再只是一个工具，而开始变成一套系统。</strong></p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">5. Memory Layer：为什么要有 CLAUDE.md</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">第五层讲的是记忆。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这也是很多人容易忽略的一层。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">因为如果你每次都重新告诉 Claude 一遍：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 组件命名规范</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 项目结构要求</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 不允许新增依赖</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 哪些工具优先使用</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">那你其实一直停留在“重复输入”的阶段。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">而作者给出的做法是，把这些长期规则沉淀到 <code class="codespan" style="font-size: 90%; color: #d14; background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05); padding: 3px 5px; border-radius: 4px;">CLAUDE.md</code> 里，作为项目记忆。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这样做的好处非常直接：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 规则不会每轮重说</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 输出更稳定</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 团队习惯可以沉淀</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• Claude 不容易“每次换一种风格”</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文对这一层的总结也很到位：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Memory converts randomness into consistency.</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">也就是说，记忆系统的真正作用，不是“让 AI 看起来更聪明”，而是让它别那么随机。</p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">6. Constraint Layer：约束不是限制，而是聚焦</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">最后一层，是约束。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">很多人给 Claude 的任务之所以越跑越歪，不是因为模型差，而是因为边界不够清楚。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">比如“做一个认证系统”这种需求，如果不给约束，它有一百种可能走法。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">但如果你明确说：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 只能用 JWT</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 不能引入外部认证提供商</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 不能改数据库结构</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 只能走现有 API 路由</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">那么 Claude 的输出空间就会立刻收敛。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">原文说得很准确：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Constraints don’t limit AI. They focus it.</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这句话特别值得反复看。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">很多人误以为“限制少一点，AI 发挥更大”，但工程里往往恰恰相反：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">限制越清楚，结果越可控。</p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">这篇文章真正改变人的地方，不是技巧，而是思维方式</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">我觉得这篇文章最重要的地方，不是教你某个 prompt 模板怎么写，而是把很多开发者的工作视角整个往前推了一步。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">以前我们想的是：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 怎么让 Claude 这次写对</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">现在应该开始想的是：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 怎么设计一个环境，让正确输出更容易发生</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这是两个完全不同的层级。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">前者是在调输出。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">后者是在搭系统。</p><h2 class="h2" data-heading="true" style="display: block; padding: 0.2em 0; padding-bottom: 0; margin: 0 auto 20px; width: 100%; color: #A93226; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.7; border-bottom: 2px solid #E4B1A0; text-align: left;">最后总结</h2><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">如果把整篇文章压缩成一句话，我会这样说：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Claude Code 最强的地方，不是它一次能写出多少代码，而是你能不能为它搭出一套让“正确结果变成默认结果”的系统。</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">所以，真正值得升级的，不是你的措辞技巧，而是下面这些能力：</p><ul class="ul" style="list-style: circle; padding-left: 1em; margin-left: 0; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2;"><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 结构化输入</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 推理分层</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 测试回流</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 项目记忆</li><li class="listitem" style="display: block; margin: 0.2em 8px; color: #3f3f3f;">• 清晰约束</li></ul><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">当你开始这么用 Claude Code，你就不再是在“向 AI 提要求”，而是在“编排一套可持续工作的智能系统”。</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">这也是原文最后那句最值得带走的话：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">Stop asking Claude to write code. Start designing systems that make code inevitable.</strong></p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">翻成中文就是：</p><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;"><strong style="color: #A93226; font-weight: bold; font-size: inherit;">别再只是让 Claude 写代码。开始去设计那些“让好代码必然出现”的系统。</strong></p><hr class="hr" style="border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 0 0; border-color: #E4B1A0; margin: 1.5em 0;"><p class="p" style="margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #3f3f3f; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; word-break: break-all;">说明：<br>这篇公众号版基于你提供的原文全文整理改写，不是逐句硬译，而是按照中文读者更容易吸收的逻辑重新组织。</p>
    
  
    
  
    
